# CODEOWNERS File for Malnu Backend
#
# This file defines who owns and must approve changes to different parts of the codebase.
# Owners are listed as GitHub usernames (e.g., @username).
#
# Format:
#   <file-pattern> <owner1> <owner2> ...
#
# Patterns:
#   - Use * for wildcard (matches any string)
#   - Use /** for recursive directory matching
#   - Lines starting with # are comments
#
# Ownership Levels:
#   - Single owner: That person must approve changes
#   - Multiple owners: Any one of them can approve
#   - @team: All members of the team can approve

